Gerda Blees, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/40/9781642861273" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>We Are Light</em></a> (World Editions)</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>CENTER FOR FICTION FIRST NOVEL PRIZE</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em>An annual award presented by The Center for Fiction, a non-profit organization in New York City, for the best debut novel.</em><br />
<em>Prize money: $10,000</em></p>
<p><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/40/9781685970000" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="135235" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/the-14-best-book-covers-of-march/norton_0303_foreign-bodies_ad-ingsu-liu_design-by-yang-kim/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/NORTON_0303_Foreign-Bodies_AD-Ingsu-Liu_Design-by-Yang-Kim.jpg" data-orig-size="1650,2475" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Kimiko Hahn, &lt;em&gt;Foreign Bodies&lt;/em&gt;; cover design by Yang Kim, art direction by Ingsu Liu (W. W. Norton, March 3)" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="&lt;p&gt;Kimiko Hahn, &lt;em&gt;Foreign Bodies&lt;/em&gt;; cover design by Yang Kim, art direction by Ingsu Liu (W. W. Norton, March 3)&lt;/p&gt;
